# MCOA — .gitignore
# Created 2026-05-08 as part of audit P0 fixes (cross-project synthesis #4: binary artifacts).

# Rust build artifacts
target/
**/target/
Cargo.lock

# Phoenix/Elixir
_build/
deps/
.elixir_ls/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# Binary artifacts (audit P0 #4)
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.pptx
*.pdf
results/*.png
results/*.jpg

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Public-repo rule (если будет публичная зеркалка): только README.md
# New .md must be added explicitly: git add -f file.md
# *.md
# !README.md
